Utterances

This board is for the sharing of ideas, questions, thoughts, facts and any other utterances related to literature or the literary life.

Please note that while any text constitutes an utterance, not all utterances need to be posted to this board. We have another board for mindless chatter. With that said, anything goes, let 'er rip, and please be nice.
